{{#page-description title='Combo Box'}}
  Standard combo box setting an attribute
  <pre><code>
    \{{combo-box
      key='code'
      searchKeys='code'
      value=model.value.option
      options=model.options
      emptyText='No options found'
    }}
  </code></pre>
  Search only combo box setting a relationship
  <pre><code>
    \{{combo-box
      searchOnly=true
      searchKeys='name,code'
      placeholder='Select an option…'
      value=model.relationship
      options=model.options
    }}
  </code></pre>
  Search only combo box setting a relationship with updater
  <pre><code>
    \{{combo-box
      searchOnly=true
      searchKeys='name,code'
      placeholder='Select an option…'
      value=model.relationship
      options=newOptions
      emptyButtonText='Click to update options'
      emptyButtonAction=(action 'updateOptions')
      isLoading=isUpdating
    }}
  </code></pre>

  <p>
    Props:
    <ul>
      <li><b>key</b>: string (optional)</li>
      <li><b>options</b>: Array (required)</li>
      <li><b>searchKeys</b>: String (required)</li>
      <li><b>value</b>: Object or attribute (required)</li>
      <li><b>placeholder:</b> String (optional)</li>
      <li><b>separator:</b> String (optional)</li>
      <li><b>emptyButtonText</b>: String (required for emptyButtonAction)</li>
      <li><b>emptyButtonAction</b>: Action (required for emptyButtonText)</li>
      <li><b>emptyText</b>: String (optional)</li>
      <li><b>isLoading</b>: Boolean (optional)</li>
      <li><b>searchOnly</b>: Boolean (optional)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      key:<br>
        The key you want to use from your options array. Defaults to name. Not used if you provide a plain object value to the component.<br><br>
      options:<br>
        The options array for selecting from.<br><br>
      searchKeys:<br>
        The keys you want to search with from your options array. The order the keys are supplied determines the display string.<br><br>
      separator:<br>
        When using multiple search keys, this defines the visual key separator. Defaults to " - ".<br><br>
      value:<br>
        The value you are setting. This can be either ember object (for relationships) or an ember object attribute.<br><br>
      emptyButtonText:<br>
        The optional button text which appears when there are no found options.<br><br>
      emptyButtonAction:<br>
        The optional button action which appears when there are no found options.<br><br>
      emptyText:<br>
        The optional empty text which appears when there are no found options.<br><br>
      isLoading:<br>
        The optional boolean that toggles the loading state.<br><br>
      searchOnly:<br>
        The optional boolean that prevents the component from being able to create its own values.<br><br>
    </p>
  </p>

